headline: Dell Boosts Long-Term Guidance. The Stock Is Rising.
summary: Dell Technologies  stock was rising Tuesday after the company boosted its long-term financial guidance, citing demand for artificial-intelligence infrastructure.  The company is targeting annual revenue growth of 7% to 9%, up from a previous range of 3% to 4%.  Dell stock was rising 2.8% to $149.90, putting it on track for a new 52-week closing high.
